head.title: Meetup RSVPs v2

item.comments: Sound like great topics, but I'm already committed to go to the Go language presentation tonight.
If you translate BEL to RDF, you can integrate it with BioPAX/SBPAX
I'm very dissapointed to miss this.

I hope to learn: Are there SWRL or RIF BLD implementations that simplify to produce an intensional result? We would like to use one of them as an access control language (I hate XACML), but need a "What if" capability -- driven by partial input.
